{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":86,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"嫣然妹她们到城外试马，准备明天田猎时大显身手，我有点不舒服，没有陪她们去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":145,"line_start":2,"line_end":3},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"琴太傅身体无恙吧？","tone":"疑问","chapter":145,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"没有什么！只是昨夜睡不好吧！","tone":"淡然","chapter":145,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我有点担心，昨天黄昏时我由王宫返来，遇上到咸阳来参加田猎的高陵君，打了个招呼，他表现得很神气，真怕他会弄出事来。","tone":"担心","chapter":145,"line_start":10,"line_end":11},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"或者是琴清多疑，有你保护储君，我还有什么不放心哩！","tone":"微笑","chapter":145,"line_start":20,"line_end":21},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"昨天陪太后共膳，那讨厌的嫪毐整天在身旁团团转，恶形恶相，真不明白太后为何视他如珠如宝。","tone":"无奈","chapter":145,"line_start":30,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"他是名副其实的'金玉其外，败絮其中'，可惜没有多少人像琴太傅般，可看穿其中的败絮。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":145,"line_start":34,"line_end":35},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"难怪嫣然妹说和你交谈，永远有新鲜和发人深省的话题儿，永远都不会听得厌倦哩！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":145,"line_start":38,"line_end":39},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"琴太傅是否有同感？","tone":"疑问","chapter":145,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项统领吃过午膳吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":145,"line_start":52,"line_end":52},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"吃过了！","tone":"陈述","chapter":145,"line_start":54,"line_end":54},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"终给我抓着统领说的谎话，现在才巳时，哪有这么早开午膳的？不想陪琴清共膳，找个什么公务繁忙的借口，便不用给琴清当场揭破。","tone":"调侃","chapter":145,"line_start":56,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我没时间理会你，现在琴清要把膳食送往城外给你的众娇妻们，项统领当然没有空一道去吧！","tone":"陈述","chapter":145,"line_start":64,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"确是有些事……嘿！琴太傅请见谅。","tone":"慌张","chapter":145,"line_start":68,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_qin_qing","speaker_name":"琴清","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项统领请！","tone":"淡然","chapter":145,"line_start":72,"line_end":73},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"琴太傅！小心走路。","tone":"低语","chapter":145,"line_start":80,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_qin_qing","text":"请恕项少龙无礼，琴太傅不用送客了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":145,"line_start":86,"line_end":88}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":["项统领"],"identity":"秦禁卫军统领","faction":"秦国","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"秦国禁卫军统领，来自未来的穿越者，智勇双全","personality":{"traits":["机智","风流","重情义","善于应变","外表粗犷内心细腻"],"speech_style":"随和幽默，偶尔调侃","temperament":"外向豁达"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_qin_qing","type":"恋人","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"暧昧升温"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[145],"source_refs":[{"chapter":145,"line_start":6,"line_end":6,"text":"项少龙关心地道"}]},{"id":"char_qin_qing","name":"琴清","alias":["琴太傅","寡妇清"],"identity":"秦国太傅","faction":"秦国","role":"companion","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"秦国太傅，清冷美丽的成熟女性，才学出众，对项少龙暗生情愫","personality":{"traits":["清冷端庄","聪慧敏锐","外冷内热","矜持","知书达理"],"speech_style":"文雅得体，偶尔流露俏皮","temperament":"温婉内敛"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"暧昧升温"},{"target":"char_ji_yan_ran","